title: I'm A Celebrity's Ash takes a stab at Keira's lips | Daily Mail Online
text: Share 26 shares 'You're like the second or third person that's asked me. You can tell when someone's had them done,' Ash responded casually. Body-confident Keira piped up: 'I've had them done'. 'You're like the second or third person that's asked me': Ash denied having had lip injections after being quizzed by Keira, who was more than happy to divulge that she had lip injections Shots fired! 'I've always wanted to be perfect!' she told the magazine, while admitting to Botox, vampire facials, lip fillers and tattooed eyebrows.' She also revealed that she's thinking of having a breast augmentation next. 'Maybe just boosting them to little teardrops, not big bazookas,' mused the Eastern Suburbs socialite.
